<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12980</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19873</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天，孩子们沿着铁路边的栏杆走在山坡上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19873</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25859</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>地面上有很多石头，但也长了很多小树和花草。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25859</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们在找野生的樱桃。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33008</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，他们听到一个声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33008</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35727</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>声音很小，但是很清晰。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35727</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38860</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>慢慢地，声音越来越大。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38860</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42771</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快看那棵树！”彼得大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42771</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47912</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女孩儿们看到一棵树慢慢地从山坡上滑了下来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47912</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52665</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>快要滑到铁路上了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52665</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56056</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是魔法！”菲利斯说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56056</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59621</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我就知道这条铁路有魔法！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59621</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63627</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>快看，其他树也在移动！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63627</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66558</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>确实看上去像是有魔法——</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66558</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71048</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有的树好像都在沿着山坡往下滑！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71048</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74529</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它们发出了巨大的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74529</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80099</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好可怕呀。我们回家吧！”菲利斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80099</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是他们还是一起看着树从山坡上滑下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89804</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接着，一些石头和土也开始松动，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89804</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>落在了下面的铁轨上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96720</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一块大石头也滚了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99632</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“全部都要滑下去了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99632</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104239</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得想说话，但吓得说不出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104239</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111012</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>更多的石头、草、树和灌木丛从山坡上滑到铁轨上，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111012</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>到处都是灰尘。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118928</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“铁轨被挡住了！”菲利斯大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118928</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120996</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是啊。”彼得说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120997</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他在思考。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127255</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“11点29分的火车还没有经过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127255</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129880</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们必须让火车站的人知道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129880</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133910</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不然就会有事故发生。”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133910</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138096</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有时间了！”菲利斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138096</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在已经过11点了。”彼得说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144414</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们想了一会儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144414</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们需要红色的东西来吸引注意力。”彼得说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149246</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这样我们就可以下去向火车挥手。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们开始向山脚下走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159595</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比脸色苍白，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159595</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163524</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>菲利斯紧张得脸都红了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163524</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166473</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我好热！”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166473</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还以为今天会很冷，早知道不穿……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175666</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她突然停了下来，看上去很兴奋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175666</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178776</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们的衬裙！”菲利斯大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178776</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“衬裙是红色的！我们脱下来吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女孩儿们脱掉衬裙，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189158</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们跑到铁路拐弯的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189158</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191765</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>火车就要来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191765</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“来吧。”彼得拿起最大的衬裙说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195917</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201177</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你该不会……是要把它撕开吧？”菲利斯问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201177</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204350</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“菲利斯，如果我们不能让火车停下来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204350</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就会出事故，有人会死的！”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212916</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得把每条衬裙都撕成三片。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212916</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215457</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他又看了看手表，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215457</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“只有七分钟了，我们还需要一些棍子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220054</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224711</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们找到一些棍子，把衬裙绑在上面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224711</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，他们有了六面红色的旗子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232979</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们在铁轨两边堆了两堆石头，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232979</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在每堆石头上都插了一面旗子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236517</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241066</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>菲利斯和鲍比一人拿了一面旗子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241066</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246392</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我拿两面，因为是我把衬裙撕开的。”彼得说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246392</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250431</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但那是我们的衬裙。”菲利斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250431</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252473</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比打断了他们，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252473</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256181</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这些都不重要！我们要拯救火车！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256181</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258855</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可能是彼得的手表走得慢，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258855</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>也可能是火车来晚了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269531</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们觉得等了很久很久。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>